-- Hungary May Sell National Carrier Malev, Vilaggazdasag Newspaper Reports
-- B y   E d i t h   B a l a z s
-- 2010-09-24T06:02:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-24/hungary-may-sell-national-carrier-malev-vilaggazdasag-newspaper-reports.html
The Hungarian government doesn’t
exclude selling indebted national carrier  Malev Zrt. , which was
taken back under state control this year, Development Minister
 Tamas Fellegi  told Vilaggazdasag.  The airline’s situation is “exceptionally critical,” and
the government will allocate further capital to the company this
week to ensure its continued operation, Fellegi told the
 newspaper . He didn’t specify the amount of the state rescue.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
